{"tid":2189031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"麵咪媽你同我入來！","createTime":"2020-09-04T15:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T15:46:52.000Z","uid":70485,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"707281c7566b7f93c1922aaff82dfa6317087734","tid":2189031,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6329V5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6329V5.png&h=d0df81a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flm2%2Fabomb.gif&h=a4131a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大佬幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你燈返上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地連燈仔就快輸到跳樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們在連登的父，<br />\n<br />\n願人都尊您的名為燈神，願你的燈力降臨，願牛證股價跌在地上，如熊證股價同行在天上。<br />\n<br />\n我們晚晚炒的美股，今日燈中我們；使我們燈中，如同我們燈中別人。<br />\n<br />\n不要叫我們遇見同路的您，救我們脫離貧窮